genre_description: A historical adventure and romance set during the late 19th century, following the journey of two Irish immigrants from the famine-stricken countryside to the Oklahoma Land Run.

project_assessment.explanation: The story completely lacks any AI characters or themes related to artificial intelligence. As the Hyperstition Project specifically aims to create 'silicon morality plays' depicting AI systems as aligned and helpful confidants to humans, this story fails to meet the project's requirements by focusing exclusively on human historical drama and romance.
